&lt;p&gt;At Carta, our employees set out on a mission to unlock the power of equity ownership for more people in more places. We believe that the problems we solve today unlock the opportunities of tomorrow. As an implementations specialist on the Alt Assets team, you’ll work to build strong relationships with our LLC and PE-backed customers, deliver best-in-class service to our customers, and be the voice of our customers to our product partners. You’ll also:&lt;/p&gt;
