&lt;p&gt;At Carta, our employees set out on a mission to unlock the power of equity ownership for more people in more places. We believe that the problems we solve today unlock the opportunities of tomorrow. As a Manager, supporting the Fund Admin Growth sales team, you’ll work to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide directional leadership for Growth AE’s by overseeing daily activities and quota performance management in order to consistently meet/exceed individual and team goals quarterly and annually&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as an internal advisor, leader, and advocate for team members&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish best practices for how to effectively manage a Growth Account Executive team and their book of business and develop and implement new sales initiatives, strategies and programs to help increase your team’s productivity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable teams to educate customers in all segments on Carta’s broader mission of creating owners&lt;/li&gt;
