&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Senior GRC Analyst&lt;/strong&gt;,&amp;nbsp; you’ll work to assess regulatory requirements and accordingly establish and maintain&amp;nbsp; governance and risk frameworks. You will build and run security compliance programs to measure and reduce risk, report compliance metrics, and build and manage policies and standards.&lt;/p&gt;
