&lt;li&gt;Manage risk program activities including risk identification, tracking, and prioritization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with engineering and product teams to assess risk posture and compliance status, and support remediation activities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
