&lt;p&gt;You will be part of a security-minded team that believes in progress over perfection and where security culture and mindset is key. Our team is rethinking how GRC activities can be accomplished in innovative ways. We do not focus on building processes, but instead how to solve business problems while minimizing and managing risk exposure for Carta.&lt;/p&gt;
