&lt;li&gt;Excellent judgment and the ability to make balanced&amp;nbsp; decisions when working with complex situations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven understanding of public cloud infrastructure and services in AWS and GCP including knowledge of cloud-native security protection measures, tools, and techniques&lt;/li&gt;
