&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Problems You&#39;ll Solve&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Carta, our employees set out on a mission to unlock the power of equity ownership for more people in more places. We believe that the problems we solve today unlock the opportunities of tomorrow. As a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Program Manager&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll work to:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lead Annual &amp;amp; Quarterly Marketing Planning&lt;/strong&gt;: Drive the planning and prioritization process for the marketing team, aligning strategy with tactical execution, spending, and ROI goals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Manage Integrated Plays and Campaigns: &lt;/strong&gt;Lead the planning and collaboration process for integrated initiatives across cross-functional marketing and revenue teams, facilitating clear strategy, high quality deliverables and on-time execution across multiple stakeholders and teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prioritize and Facilitate Channel Execution: &lt;/strong&gt;Support internal customers of virtual and live events, lifecycle, community, and performance marketing by building and socializing processes that prioritize highest-impact initiatives and streamline collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manage Planning Calendar for Priority Plays, Campaign and Initiatives&lt;/strong&gt;: Drive a hyper cross-functional planning process for quarterly integrated marketing plays, priorities, and budgets with a focus on near term and long term roadmaps.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Facilitate Key Decision Points&lt;/strong&gt;: Identify critical decision moments during program execution, aligning teams and resources to ensure smooth progress and timely resolutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monitor &amp;amp; Report Performance&lt;/strong&gt;: Collect, analyze, and report on key metrics and deliverables, using data to evaluate performance and inform future marketing plans.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate Across Teams&lt;/strong&gt;: Work closely with content, product marketing, performance marketing, growth, revenue, and GTM/marketing operations to ensure program and campaign goals are met. Work across global marketing partners to expand our reach.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Project Manage Marketing Campaigns and Experiments&lt;/strong&gt;: Build project plans and oversee campaigns, ensuring clear deliverables, deadlines, and high-quality, on-time launches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The senior program manager plays a critical role in planning for the marketing team and collaborating across multiple functions to ensure efficient execution of marketing strategy. This role is a strong partner for marketers with stakeholders including, Product Marketing, Customer Marketing, Demand Gen, MOps, Sales/Business Development and Strategy/Biz Ops.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A rigorous approach to mastering complexity is a must, without sacrificing empathy and flexibility for unplanned needs that can be required in a dynamic environment.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A strategic and analytical thinker who can connect programs/projects to business priorities&lt;/li&gt;
