&lt;li&gt;6-8+ years experience in program or project management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in working with Asana or equivalent platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;BA required&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
